text: Anton Kamenev (born 15 January 1986) is a Russian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined team event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Russia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
